  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2200968">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2200968/" class="title-link">内幕内幕</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2200968"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/philobiblon/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2096076-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/philobiblon/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">尔狮山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-06"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-06 09:07:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2200968_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我看的是85年2月第二版的，91年10月第三次印刷。 结合着刚看过的《潜伏》，由于不太详细了解当时的大背景，读读这本书里的内容，可以给予补充了解。 刚刚百度了一下，沈醉老人已于96年去世。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2200968_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2200968_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1923393">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1923393/" class="title-link">想探究这些降将的心理</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1923393"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhangjingxia/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhangjingxia/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">清风拂面慰我心</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-03-24"
      class="main-meta">2009-03-24 11:10:47</span>
