  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3318419">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3318419/" class="title-link">细节</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3318419"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/claymoreteresa/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4316980-64.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/claymoreteresa/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">联合帝国</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-09"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-09 09:53:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3318419_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  沈醉在书中写军统内部如何押解其有问题的成员时描述为：明明是A去逮捕B，却指示让B把A押解到指定地点，到了指定地点，A却突然出示逮捕手续将B逮捕。书中许多特工行事的细节甚为有趣，至于立场，沈已是降将，想要说出一些真实看法谈何容易？

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
